38974>>>            Set psCaption to C_$ToolTipClear
38975>>>            Set peActionDisplay to adMenu            
38976>>>                        
38976>>>            Procedure OnClick
38979>>>                // this will undo any unchanged saves and show the latest
38979>>>                Send RefreshRecord
38980>>>            End_Procedure
38981>>>        End_Object 
